Purchases of Equity Securities by the Issuer
On 15 September 2011, the Board of Directors authorized the repurchase of up to $1.0 billion of our outstanding
common stock. This program does not have a stated expiration date. We repurchase shares pursuant to Rules 10b5-1
and 10b-18 under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended, through repurchase agreements established with
one or more brokers. There were no purchases of stock during fiscal year 2019. At 30 September 2019, $485.3 million
in share repurchase authorization remained. Additional purchases will be completed at the Company’s discretion while
maintaining sufficient funds for investing in its businesses and growth opportunities.
