2020 OUTLOOK
In fiscal year 2020, we intend to grow our earnings by continuing to improve our base businesses and execute against
our capital deployment strategy. Backed by our current financial position, we will strive to continue to win and invest in
key growth projects, including large gasification projects that are consistent with our onsite business model. We expect
earnings to grow from an investment in a new equity affiliate that will acquire the gasification, power, and industrial gas
assets at Jazan Economic City, Saudi Arabia ("the Jazan gas and power project").
The above guidance should be read in conjunction with the Forward-Looking Statements of this Annual Report on Form
10-K.
