In fiscal year 2018, we completed eight acquisitions that were accounted for as business combinations. These
acquisitions had total consideration, net of cash acquired, of $355.4. The largest of the acquisitions was completed
during the first quarter of fiscal year 2018 and primarily consisted of three air separation units serving onsite and
merchant customers in China, which strengthened our position in the region. The results of this business are
consolidated within our Industrial Gases – Asia segment.
