Stock Options
We have granted awards of options to purchase common stock to executives and selected employees. The exercise
price of stock options equals the market price of our stock on the date of the grant. Options generally vest incrementally
over three years and remain exercisable for ten years from the date of grant. The Company has not issued stock option
awards since fiscal year 2015.
